\id 2PE Tagin: Bible Translation 1st Edition
\h 2 Pitar
\toc1 PITAR lokv Lvnyinvbv Siti jinam
\toc2 2 Pitar
\toc3 2Pit
\mt1 PITAR
\mt2 lokv Lvnyinvbv Siti Jinam
\imt1 Mintamchonam
\ip \bk Pitar gv Lvnyinvbv siti lvknam\bk* si kvvlo lokv kristan richo kunv vdwgv lvgabv mvngla lvkdam talv toku. Soogv lvgingla lvkdam jvnam si oogv mvvlarula tamsar sarmurnv vdwgv kudungkua okv gwngmur singmurnv vdwa mvdarminsu monam lvgabv. Svkvnv mirwk lwktak minsu dula adwkaku am paakunam si Pwknvyarnv gv chinampanam okv Ahtu Jisu Kristo gv jvjvrungnv chinam am gakbwngla nyi dukunv sum, Jisu Kristonyi oogv awv Jisunyi kaakunv nyi okv ninyi bunu vdwgv tamsar kunama tvvkunv. Lvknv gv lvkdum jvnamv yvvbunudw Kristo lvkodv aaku mare vla tamsarnv vdwa lvkrwk sila lvktoku, ninyigv minamv Kristo gv chintola aakur manamv Pwknvyarnv “yvvnyika ngoomu so mvngma vbvritola bunua rimur lokv mvngdin kusvgo vla mvngyadunv.” Vkvnv siti lvknv vdwv Jisu lvkodv aaku mare vla jvjvklvbv maatar alvbv mvvla lvkdu. Hv vbv minjito Jisu Kristo gv aakur kumakv vnam si Pwknvyarnv “yvvnyika simungomu nvpv vla mvngma dunv, vbvritola mvnwng ngv adwnamar gv rimur lokv adu modukubv mvngdu vla mvvla ridu.”
\iot Arwng lokv darlinnam
\io1 Mintamchonam \ior (1:1-2) \ior*
\io1 Kristan bv goknam \ior (1:3-21) \ior*
\io1 Tamsar sarmurnv \ior (2:1-22) \ior*
\io1 Jisu Kristo gv aakur kusvlvga \ior (3:1-18) \ior*
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Jisu Kristo gv pakbu akobv rinv okv ngo Apostol Simon Pitar lokv—
\p Ngonugv aingbv Pwknvyarnv gvlo tarwkbak yachoknv lamtv lokv okv ngonugv ringnvbaanv Jisu Kristo gv lokv arvdoya choknv mvngjwng jinam vdwlo kumrwksinam gaamv:
\p 
\v 2 Pwknvyarnv okv ngonugv Ahtu Jisunyi nonugv chinam lokv nonu gvlo akomaring bv anyuaya namv okv sarsopoyo namv doolwk yilaka.
\s1 Pwknvyarnv gv gakla okv goknam
\p 
\v 3 Yvvdw ngonua ninyigv yunglit okv alvnam baak dubv\f + \fr 1:3 \fqa Ninyigv yunglit okv alvnam baak; \ft Kvvgonv kitap lo doodu \fqa Ninyigv gv lokv.\f* vla ngonua goknv, um ngonu chinggv rila jvjvnv dormo singdunglo singnam lvgabv ogu ogugo dinchi pvkudw ho mvnwng nga Pwknvyarnv gv kairungnv jwkrwa ngonua jitoku.
\v 4 Svkvnv lamtv lo hv milvkunam lo arv doyachoknv okv achialv bv kainv amin am jitoku, svbv amin jiku sokv nonu nyiamooku sokv yonwngla mvyakmvchak nam lokv kilin dukubv, okv Pwknvyarnv ridung nga paaming gvvdu kubv.
\v 5 Holvgabv vbvrinamv nonugv lvgvlvma lokv nonugv mvngjwng lo alvnam am lwkpwng toka; nonugv alvnv chingkikpakik nama lwkpwng toka.
\v 6 Nonugv chingkikpakik nam lokv saktv nvnvlo lwkpwng toka; nonugv saktvnam lokv himv gvnvlo lwkpwng toka; nonugv himvnam lokv Pwknvyarnv mvngnam am lwkpwng toka;
\v 7 nonugv Pwknvyarnv mvngnam lokv kristan pakmi sinama lwkpwng toka; okv nonugv kristan pakmi sinam lokv paknama lwkpwng toka.
\v 8 Sikvnv alamai am nonu dinchi svngv, okv nonu gvlo bunua doolwk mobolo, vv bunu nonua ngonu Ahtu Jisu Kristo gv chingkikpakik am nonu gvlo asaryaung more okv chvrv more.
\v 9 Vbvritola soogv vdwsi yvvbunu gvlo dooma dudw bunu abwkajek mabv ho nonu kaapa nyomadu okv nonugv kvvlo rimur rikunam am kakpung kunam am mvngpa kuma duku.
\p 
\v 10 Vkvlvgabv, ngoogv ajin vdw, nonua Pwknvyarnv gv goknam am okv ninyigv gaknam am doobwng rungdubv ritolaka; holvgabv svkvnv sum nonu vbvribolo nonugv mvngjwng nam sum vdwloka kayu mare.\f + \fr 1:10 \fqa Nonugv mvngjwng nam sum vdwloka kayu mare; \ft Vmalo \fqa Rimur lo holunam. \f*
\v 11 Svkvnv riku lamtv lokv nonugv Ahtu okv ringnv Jisu Kristo gv turbwngjiku karv lo aala dubv Pwknvyarnv jire.
\p 
\v 12 Okv nonu vdwv jvjvrungnv sum adakrungbv hargap pvvla laarwk pvvsudu okv bunua chinpvvla doodu vbvrijvka svkvnv sum ngo nonua mvngpa la ribvre.
\v 13 Ngoogv turyi dvdv so svkvnv vdw sum nonuam mimpa yala miyar yanam si ngoogv tarwkbaknv kudungkua ngv vla mvngsu dunv.
\v 14 Ngonugv Ahtu Jisu gv nga mindalvpa bv minjinam aingbv, ngoogv so nyejikunv adwnamar sum kayu yiku nvpv vla ngo chinsudu.
\v 15 Vbvrikunamv, ngoogv siro kokwng lojvka svkvnv sum nonu lvgabv mvngpa bvbv sila dubv, ngo vdwgo lvgvlvmabv risv vdw vkvgo rila vvpv jire.
\s1 Kristo gv yunglit am kaanv mvnwng ngv
\p 
\v 16 Ngonu Ahtu Jisu Kristo gv kairungbv aasv nga chimu dubv vla mvnammvsubv higu mvnam vdwa mvngging madunv. Ninyigv Kairungnv am ngonu nyikdadw lo kaatar lwknam lokv minji doonv.
\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt Mt 17:1-5; Mk 9:2-7; Lk 9:28-35\x* Vdwlo hv mvngdv okv yunglit nama, Pwknvyarnv Abu gv lokv jito kubvdw ngonu hoka dooto, vdwlo ninyia vlvgo aala Kaiyachokbv Yunglit kunv gv lokv vbv minjila, “Si ngoogv Paknam Kuunyilo ngv, ngo ninyia alvrungbv mvngpu dunv!”
\v 18 Vdwlo ngonu darwknv moodw lo ninyigv lvkobv doola riyilo, ngonu atubongv awv soogv vlv nga nyidomooku lokv aadu bv tvvtar lwkto.
\p 
\v 19 Vbvrikunamv nyijwk vdwgv doin japgo kunama ngonu alvyabv mvngjwng yaya duku. Nonu svkvnv sum alvjvbv tvvgap suto laka, ogulvgavbolo Sikvnv si mvdurupum aingbv ridu oogv kanvparam lo loung bv arupua lobv hunglwknam apiabv okv nonugv haapoklo arukamchi gv karlumpumbum loung ngv hunglwkdu.
\v 20 Ogubvrijvka, mvnwng gv aolo sum mvnggap tvlaka yvvka Darwknv Kitap lo nyijwk vdwgv nyikrw kaanama atubogv yvvka minbwk jila nyumare.
\v 21 Vkvlvgavbolo nyijwk vdwgv doin milwk minamv vdwloka nyia mvngnam lokv aamato, vbvritola Pwknvyarnv gvlokv aanv doina nyi vdwgv japyilo japnv vdwv Darwknv Dow gv arwnglo doonyato.
\c 2
\s1 Tamsar sarmurnv vdw.
\p 
\v 1 Nyijwk mvvnvrunv vdwv nyi vdwgv pingkolo kvvlo lokv aacho toku, okv oogv apiabv tamsar sarmurnv vdwka nonugv pingkolo aare. Bunu vdwv mvvkmvrvk nam, jvjvmanv doin mintam nvnga aagvre, okv bunua oogv ringlin kunv Ahtu um minala rire, okv vkvlgabv bunu awv atubogv aolo dvminmabv mvyakmvchak nama laalwk sure.
\v 2 Vbvrikwng jvka achialvgonv bunugv gwngmur singmur lamtv lo vngming gvvla rire; okv bunu ogu ridudw vkvlvkwnglo, kvvbi nyi vdwgv Jvjvnv Lamtv am alvmanv bv mvvnam mvvreku.
\v 3 Bunugv kabiotarinv lokv miriukminda la higunai vngji dula soogv mvvla tamsar sarmurnv vdwv nonuam boksi minlin la rire. Holvgabv klu lokv lalayikula vjvgobv bunu vdwa Jwngkadaka jinv ngv mvpvripv duku, okv bunugv mvyakmvchak kuji nvngv yumabv uula doyala riduku!
\p 
\v 4 Oogv rimurnv nyidogindung vdwa Pwknvyarnv yvvnyika kayu mabv, vbvritola bunua uyumooku gv kanvparam bolo leetola, \f + \fr 2:4 \fqa Kanvparam bolo leetola; \ft Kitap kvgonvlo doodu; \fqa Kanvparam lo takpvdu. \f* Jwngkadakadw aluv aama dadw lo gobv, bunua paalwk nyala ritoku.
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt Atk 6:1—7:24\x* Pwknvyarnv klugv akunv nyiamookua kayula rimato, vbvridula oogv darwkmanv nyi vdwgv nyiamookua svdwng nga tvvlu jila rimu toku; vbvritola oogv darwkchongjor nama japgola rinv akingo Nua, okv kvvbi nyi kanw mvngchikgo ringlin mvngchik toku.
\v 6 \x - \xo 2:6 \xt Atk 19:24\x* Pwknvyarnv Sodom okv Gomorra pamtv am mvyakmvchak la rito, bunua vmv lokv taayuk jukjuk toku, okv vbv Pwknvyarnvnyi chimabv rinv vdwa ogubv ritv dunvdw um bunua kaagv sinv dubv mvtoku.
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt Atk 19:1-16\x* Okv alvnv nyi go Lotnyi oogv pvbvkaamanv nyi vdwgv gwngmurrimur rigvnam lokv mvngdwk yanv um Pwknvyarnv ringlin jilaku ritoku.
\v 8 Oogv alvnv nyigo bunugv aralo doonamv, bunugv alvmabv rinam am tvvla okv kaala yikula hv aluguya guya mvngdwk yala ridu.
\v 9 Okv holvgabv Ahtu darwknv nyi vdwa adwk akunam lokv oguaingbv ringlin svngvdw okv oguaingbv alvmanv vdwa Jwngkadakadw alulo mvrit nam lvgabv arwnglo apv svngvdw um chindu,
\v 10 yvvdw Pwknvyarnv gv tujupkunam am tvvma yabv okv adwnamar gv dvnwngyonwng lo riming gvvdudw um bunua vvpvre.
\p Soogv tamsar sarmurnv vdwsi busukano go kaamadu okv mimbo sulaka ridu, okv aolo doonv yunglitnv vdw lvgabvka mvngdv namgo kaatam jimadu; vbvmayabv, bunua nyarjitari la riyadu.
\v 11 Nyidogindung vdwv, oogv tamsar sarmurnv vdwa gwlwkyadu okv kaiyanv bvka ridu vbvrijvka, bunu vdwa Ahtu gv kaagelo yamla minjimiyo la rinamgo kaamadu.
\v 12 Vbvritola oogv nyi vdwv kudungkua yartak nambv rirungdu, mootum lokv svnwngsvmin anga aingbv laatung la okv pakila rinyato; Bunu mvnvmvrvla ogumvnwng nga mvki dubv ridu bunu mvngchin madu. Bunu vdwa mootum gv svnwngsvmin aingbv mvki riku,
\v 13 okv bunu alvmabv rinv lvgabv alvmabv ridu kalamre. Bunugv mvngpu nam lvgabv ogumvnwng am alu gv loung lo ogu ridudw ho bunugv adwnamar gv nyumchi namv; Bunugv kupnam lamtv mvnwng am himpu sigv dula, nonugvlo lvkingobv aala dvbamtvngbam la rinamv nonugv hinyinghiru namgobv ridu!
\v 14 Bunu yvvnyika mvnggya madu vbvritola randwbajilo rinv nyimv nga mvnggya la ridu; Bunu gvlo rimur sinam lvgabv kano ngv vdwloka nyumchi madu. Bunu agiam anyum dunv nyi am amin lo rikup lwkdu. Bunugv haapok am gumpwng dubv risarsila ridu. Bunu Pwknvyarnv gv beenam arwnglo doodukunv!
\v 15 \x - \xo 2:15,16 \xt Num 22:4-35\x* Bunu sursinv lamtv nga kayuto okv bunugv lamtv ngam nyeemu tvku; Bunu oogv alvmanv kudungkua lo rigvla morko gv paanam kudungkua nga alvbv yabv mvngnv, Beor gv kuu Balaam gv lamtv vngkulo vngming gvvto
\v 16 okv ninyigv svnwngpvcha ngv nyi ako gv gaambv milin jidula nyijwk vdwgv svrudurak la kudungkua ritvkunam am mintor toku. Okv ninyigv rimur kunam lvgabv mintor la ritoku.
\p 
\v 17 Soogv nyi vdwv isi sigung lo sintar kunam aingbv ridukunv, doogumdori gv mibv nam doomwk bv ridunv; Pwknvyarnv bunu lvgabv kanvparam arwngnv mooku go laapv jito.
\v 18 Bunu vdwv kaimvngsuto okv pvchaaria gaambv mindu, okv oogv alvmabv rinv nyi vdwgv pingko lokv vjakpiak bv kisuk linpinv vdwa adwnamar bv dvnwngyonwng rimurriche lo rinvvngnv dubv vla kupla ridu.
\v 19 Bunu sijiku kogv lamtv ridung gv nyira bv ridula bunua ajarabi jimu nvpv vla milv la ridu—vkvlvgavbolo ngonu yvvdw ogumvnwng nga riyayaku dudw ngonu oogv nyira bv ridukunv.
\v 20 Nyi vdwv Jisu Kristonyi ringnv okv ngonugv Ahtu gobv bunugv vbv chingku lokv nyiamooku sokv alvmanv gv nyi vdwgv lokv kisuk lindu kula, okv bunu lvkodv rigum yakula ribolo, vkvnv nyi vdwv kvvlo lokv richo yanv amum svnga alvmaya rinvpv.
\v 21 Bunua darwknv rinam lamtv nga chimula rimu tvkula, darwknv orto jiku nama bunugv vngkur gvla rimum kusvnga, vdwloka bunua darwkbv rinam lamtv nga chimu manamv alvyago kunyikv.
\v 22 \x - \xo 2:22 \xt Nyit 26:11\x* Bunua ogugo ripvdw kaatam namv oogv minjwk minkiuk namv jvjvdu: “Ikiv atubogv bvvnam am lvkodv dvkor siduku” okv “vrik v sokpung mola rijeka eeriung lo durbok dvdv duku.”
\c 3
\s1 Ahtu gv aakur kusvnga milvpvvnam
\p 
\v 1 Ngoogv ajin vdwv, vjak ngoogv siti si nonuam lvnyinvbv lvkdunv. Ngoogv siti taknyigo lvknam si nonugv haapok gv mvngnam baangv so mvngdar la prototo nam lvgabv mimpa dvdunv.
\v 2 Nonua kvvlogv darwknv nyijwk vdwgv gamchar mincho kunam vdwa mvngpa tvkv vla ngo mvngdu okv Nonugv Apostol vdwgvlo oogv Ahtu okv ringnvbaanv gv orto jilwk kunam um mvnggap dvdv laka vla mvngdunv.
\v 3 \x - \xo 3:3 \xt Jud 18\x* Mvnwng gv atuakebv, anyung anya gv alunyi bunu awgv dvnwngyonwng nam lokv rinv nyi meego kaapa rinvpv vla nonu chirung laka. Bunu vdwv nonua nyarjitarire
\v 4 okv tvjikao la rire, “Jisu aare vla milv pvvnamv, Hv aama ai? Hv ogo lokula? Ngonugv abuapa vdwv siyu roku, vbvritola sichingmookua pwkrilo pwknamyarnam dvdv ngv ogumvnwng ngv klu lokv doonv ngv vjaklodvbv hvrak bv doobvdu.”
\v 5 \x - \xo 3:5 \xt Atk 1:6-9\x* Bunu klulo sichingmooku okv nyidomooku am Pwknvyarnv gamkigo jirungla pwklin pvnv vla, bunu jvjvbv chingrung tvla okv chimanv aingbv rirungdu. Sichingmooku sum isi agum lo laalinla okv isi lokv pwklinto,
\v 6 \x - \xo 3:6 \xt Atk 7:11\x* okv si ka isi lokv gvngv rungto, svdwng tvvlu nvngv aku kunv nyiamookua tvyak toku.
\v 7 Vbvritola nyidomooku gvla okv sichingmooku gv vjvgv doodunv sika Pwknvyarnv gv gamki kunam akin lokv doodunv, soogv doodunv si vmv lokv gupak la gua modu kubv vla dooduku. Vdwlo Pwknvyarnvnyi mvngjwng mabv doonv vdwa jwngkadaka yikudw okv um bunua nyeetak simu dukubv vla kaachingkaamu la vvpvtoku.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 3:8 \xt Miri 90:4\x* Vbvritola ngoogv ajin vdw, nonu so angv sum mvngpa mabv riyoka! Ahtu gv kaagia lo alu lookin vla okv hejar anying ngv ogu angusiya nvgo kaama dunv; ninyigv lvgabv soogv anyiv lvyin akinnv.
\v 9 Kvvgo nvgv vbv mvngnam aingbv, Ahtu Jisu ogugo hv milvpvdw um ridubv haatvgoyula rimadunv. Vbvmayabv, hv nonua lvkobv saktv minggvdu, ogulvgavbolo hv akin goka sitoka vla mvngmadu, vbvritola bunugv mvnwng nga rimur vdwlokv mvngkurla mvngdin modu kubv mvngdu.
\p 
\v 10 \x - \xo 3:10 \xt Mt 24:43; Lk 12:39; 1Tes 5:2; Nyikrw 16:15\x* Vbvritola Ahtu gv aadw Aluv dvchonv aanam aingbv aare. Oogv Alunyi nyidomooku aduv tvtak kumabv dula nyere, nyidomooku gv doonyi poolu, takar vdwv vmvbv guyakgupakla okv guyok riku, okv sichingmooku gv ogumvnwng ngvka mvyakmvchak reku.\f + \fr 3:10 \fqa Nyengam reku \ft Kvvgonv kitap lo doodu \fqa mapa tvvlaka; \ft Kvvbi vdwgvlo ka doodu \fqa Baayuk tvvlaka; \ft Akonvlo doodu \fqa Mvyakriyak dubv mapa tvvlaka. \f*
\v 11 Sibv rila ogumvnwng ngv mvyakmvpak rokubolo, nonu ogunv nyi bv riku svngvdw? Nonugv singdung nga darwk nvbv rirung tokuka okv Pwknvyarnv gvlo tulwksula ritoka,
\v 12 vbv nonu Pwknvyarnv gv aadw Alua kaayala doodubv baapubv aagor monam lvgabv nonugv lvgvlvma lokv rilaka—Alu lo nyidomookuv vmvbv gupak reku okv mvyakmvpak reku, okv nyidomooku gv doonyi, poolu, takar vdwv hagula jimwkjimak reku.
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt Aij 65:17; 66:22; Nyikrw 21:1\x* Vbvritola Pwknvyarnv ogugo milvpvdw um ngonu kaaya du: vv anwnv nyidomooku okv anwnv sichingmooku go vv darwkchongjornv naam bv rire.
\p 
\v 14 Okv vbvrikunamv, ngoogv ajin vdw, nonu vkvnv alu am kaaya dunvdw, Pwknvyarnv gv kaagialo nonu Darwkyachok nvbv okv alvyachok nvbv ritoka okv ninyigv lvkobv sarsopoyo minggv tvlaka holvgabv lvgvlvmabv rilaka.
\v 15 Ngonua ringnam lvgabv ngonugv Ahtu gv saktv nama alvnv gamdak am kaato laka, ngonugv aya minsunam Paul Pwknvyarnv gv mvngkimvnglak jinam am rinvla nonua lvknam apiabv.
\v 16 Vkv aingbv ninyigv siti lvkyi dwkibv oogv lvkwng bv vbvching naala lvkdu. Vbv lvknam lo chinyu manam vkv doodu, um chimapamunv vdwv okv kiamkarnv nyi mvnwng ngv Darwknv Kitap am baago—baago nvlo mimurla minam aingbv so siti sum mimurla minji nyadu. Vkvlvgabv bunu vdwv bunugv mvyakmvchak svnga naalwk sidu.
\p 
\v 17 Vbvrijvka, ngoogv ajin vdw, nonu sum chinro duku. Vbvrikunamv, nonu atubongv hima sulaka, vbvribolo Pvbv chimanv alvmanv nyi vdwgv rigakpanam lokv nonua riye gvla vnggv lamare okv nonu ringlin kunam lokv holu laku mare.
\v 18 Vbvritola ngonugv Ahtu okv Ringnvbaanv Jisu Kristo gv chingkikpakik namlo okv anyuaya namlo kaiyaya laka. Vjak okv dvbvdwkibv yunglitnamv ninyi gvbvka. Amen.
